Important files:
  1- STYLE: Describes the coding style for this project
  2- REQ: Describes the requirements of the project 
  3- Design: Describes the design choices of this project
  4- Lexical: Describes the lexical structure of the language we're compiling
  5- Grammar: Describes the grammar for the language we're compiling

By the way; the whole of this project is impossible to build without the Dragon
Book; most of the ideas I am using aren't mine but found in the book, you really
should give it a read.
